You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off your Philco smart products

After connecting Alexa to your Philco Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Smart Life Philco" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Smart Life Philco account in our "Smart Life Philco" app;
(3). You need to have some Philco devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Philco Smart Life" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Smart Life Philco" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Smart Philco" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Smart Life Philco", and you'll be navigated to Philco login page;
(9). Input your Philco account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on bedroom air conditioner"

Currently this skill supports products:
smart air conditioner
